FUNCTION get_instrumentTelemetry

PURPOSE: Read the raw telemetry and return as a structure

USAGE : out=get_instrumentTelemetry( [,SORT_BYTIME=sort_bytime][,VERBOSE=verbose] [,DEBUG=DEBUG])

INPUT PARAMETERS:

SORT_BYTIME : Set to sort the return structure in increasing time (default=1) VERBOSE : Set if reporting of details is desired DEBUG : Set to report additional information useful in debugging.

OUTPUT PARAMETERS: Sample Structure of telemetry products:

TIME_S DOUBLE Array[41892] TIME_MS DOUBLE Array[41892] TIME0_MS DOUBLE 9.4340165e+14 TIME0_S DOUBLE 9.4340165e+11 GRATPOS FLOAT Array[41892] COUNTS FLOAT Array[41892] TEMPS FLOAT Array[41892]
